{{version030}}
{{Flavour|Summons weapons from far and wide - a dagger newly forged, a sword long-rusted in a moldering tomb, an axe still steaming with the blood of its victim - animating them and sending them out to attack.}}

'''Sheza's Dance''' is a monster-only spell that summons 2-4 random [[dancing weapon]]s which are [[haste]]d. These weapons can boost the power of the caster's [[Resonance Strike]]. Despite the description, this spell is not limited to daggers, swords, and axes.

{{monsters with spell}}

==History==
Sheza's Dance was added in [[0.29]].

